<h3 id="管理工具">管理工具</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Jekyll official site(中文版): <a href="http://jekyllcn.com/">jekyllcn</a></li>
  <li>markdown 参考: <a href="http://kramdown.gettalong.org/quickref.html">kramdown</a></li>
  <li>关于 Hexo + gitHub另外一种方法<a href="https://volantis.js.org/">volantis</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="关于注释">关于注释</h3>
<p>Add a variable called <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">comments</code> to the <a href="http://jekyllcn.com/docs/plugins/">YAML front matter</a> and set its value to true. A sample might look like:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>---
layout: post
comments: true
# other options
---
</code></pre></div></div>

